{"tid":1345343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鍵盤戰線] 建制同港共想借元朗黑夜抹黑示威者 打好文宣戰","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:58:29.000Z","uid":112814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7f797034e2c2d0169e6f340776f1eac6986b43","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:53:22.000Z","msg":"琴晚係香港版國定殺戮日<br />\n黑狗單方面對途人無差別施襲<br />\n黑警包庇黑狗 已經毫無誠信可言<br />\n沈旭輝話依單野應屬恐怖襲擊<br />\n同時黑警係示威者撤退途中係無通知下開左幾十槍<br />\n違反警例<br />\n大家一齊打好文宣戰<br />\n大家要知道我地影響力好大 上埋Time Magazine <br />\n所以多你一把鍵盤 場仗就多一分勝算<br />\n無論係外國定本土戰場 我地都唔可以輸<br />\n要將真相話俾全世界知<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HongKongers! Assemble!<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0c089f75f71cbe8da22e7f312b805ddebb684cf9","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c29e8500dfc2949a207e2a3f0033655b3c0e1e8","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"728"},{"pid":"4380809ec8bb32925b08ff0876d25829f0c4ccf9","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f7af0857522d906f8c093b667a5ab65377b22b0e","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"82f95c109f24bdcf5abe10c7122228a34cc25c24","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士你地都好重要"},{"pid":"f4cbe976ed19f529132c6f4d59a0a7fa627832d3","tid":1345343,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":